aman.name: aman kumar
aman.description: Building digital experiences with Blockchain, AI, and Full-Stack Development.

projects.title: Check Mate
projects.description: CheckMate automates document verification with AI and blockchain, storing verified files on IPFS and providing tamper-proof access, fast verification, and a secure document wallet.

projects.title: Well Wise
projects.description: Well Wise is a healthcare platform that emphasizes mental health detection and management through AI-driven tools. it aims to tackle the challenge of diagnosing and managing depression.

projects.title: Key Vault
projects.description: KeyVault is a secure password manager built with ReactJS, Tailwind, MongoDB, Express, and Node.js. It enables biometric authentication such as (fingerprint, Face ID) and stores data in encrypted form.
